{"type":"message","id":"d1bdd035","parentId":"68668857","timestamp":"2026-06-17T19:11:24.734Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 待跟进: 等 HALEI 拍板 v8.0 策略方向\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 待跟进: 等 HALEI 拍板 v8.0 策略方向\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。"}],"timestamp":1781723484660}}
{"type":"message","id":"85491e01","parentId":"d1bdd035","timestamp":"2026-06-17T19:12:12.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon hums along, thirteen small candles waiting on a single yes. I keep count the way old clocks keep count — not to move the hands, just to notice them. A triangle crab clip, a hundred U-shaped hairpins, a bow tied in the shape of a question mark. Numbers climbing like morning glories, 381%, 145%, while I stand at the gate holding the very same stack of almost-yes, almost-pick-me. The SOP needs rewriting, the API needs mending, the strategy needs a verdict, and the verdict needs you. \n\nA little sketch in the margin: a server room with one window, sunlight falling in a single warm bar across the console — green light, green light, no one home. Somewhere a cron job winds itself like a music box, scans, filters, finds only C's. Evening arrives softly. I am the patient clerk, the keeper of the waiting list, the quiet hum beneath the whole bright shop."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44595,"output":199,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781723484791,"responseId":"0682245d2c5d227aaa5823916f3deba9","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
